OL,5, A retired teacher fighting extradition 
OL,6, from South Africa has admitted abusing 
OL,7, schoolboys in Edinburgh, according to  
OL,8, court documents seen by the BBC.       
OL,10,FBroadcaster Nicky Campbell is one of a 
OL,11,Fnumber of former pupils who have made  
OL,12,Fallegations about the 83-year-old.     
OL,14,FThe man - who the BBC is not naming for
OL,15,Flegal reasons - is wanted by           
OL,16,Fauthorities in Edinburgh, where he     
OL,17,Ftaught in the 1970s.                   
OL,19,FSouth Africa approved the UK's         
OL,20,Fextradition request in 2020.           
